# Lychee Link Checker Exclusions
# ============================

# Domains that block scrapers or return forbidden/forbidden codes in CI
https://portal.azure.com/
https://console.cloud.google.com/
https://www.sap.com/
https://hub.docker.com/

# Domains with SSL issues or unreliable availability
https://lan-play.com/

# GitHub redirects that Lychee sometimes flags
https://github.com/login.*
https://github.com/settings/personal-access-tokens/new
https://github.com/settings/tokens
https://github.com/FaserF/hassio-addons/issues/new.*

# Home Assistant documentation that might be flaky or redirected
# (Pointed to /apps/ now)

# GitHub Packages (GHCR) links that might 404 until first publish
https://github.com/FaserF/hassio-addons/pkgs/container/.*

# Home Assistant base images or private repositories that are unavailable / return 404 in CI
https://github.com/hassio-addons/addon-base/releases/tag/.*
https://github.com/FaserF/ha-webserver
https://github.com/pterodactyl/wings/releases/tag/.*
https://github.com/requarks/wiki/releases/tag/.*
